title: HOUR 1 - Aaron Rodgers, Cowboys, Niners
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Aaron Rodgers, Cowboys, Niners
description:
Thoughts on the Packers loss to the Vikings and why Aaron Rodgers needs to learn patience

The Cowboys get more bad news and more proof Dak Prescott can't elevate teammates 

Niners QB Trey Lance can't use weather as an excuse, he needs to play better

 

Guest: Greg Olsen
